短期光伏功率预测1

靳晓松

2018年10月16日

1 获取数据

setwd("E:/sprixin/power")

library(Rmisc)
library(magrittr)
library(lubridate)
library(data.table)
library(tidyverse)



train_1 <- read_csv("train_1.csv")
names(train_1) <- c('datetime', 'irradiance', 'wind_speed', 'wind_direction',
                    'temperation', 'pressure', 'humitidy', 'real_irradiance', 
                    'real_power')

train_1 %<>%
  mutate(datetime = datetime + seconds(x = 1),
         split_year = factor(year(datetime), levels = 2016:2018, ordered = T),
         split_quarter = factor(quarter(datetime), levels = 1:4, ordered = T),
         real_irradiance = ifelse(real_irradiance < 0, 0, real_irradiance))

2 探索数据

2.1 split_year & split_quarter

bar_year <-
  ggplot(train_1, aes(x = split_year, fill = split_year)) +
  geom_bar() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = 'none')

bar_quarter <-
  ggplot(train_1, aes(x = split_quarter, fill = split_quarter)) +
  geom_bar() +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = 'none')

multiplot(bar_year, bar_quarter, cols = 2)

2.2 irradiance

hist_irradiance <-
  ggplot(train_1, aes(x = irradiance)) +
  geom_histogram(fill = '#1f77b4', color = 'black') +
  theme_bw()

box_irradiance <-
  ggplot(train_1, aes(x = irradiance, y = irradiance)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  theme_bw()

multiplot(hist_irradiance, box_irradiance, cols = 2)

2.11 year & quarter & real_power

year_quarter_power <-
  ggplot(train_1, aes(x = split_quarter, y = real_power, fill = split_quarter)) +
  geom_boxplot() +
  facet_grid(. ~ split_year) +
  theme_bw() +
  theme(legend.position = 'none')
